HEADWORD: Gassy
<hw>Gas"sy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Full of
gas; like gas.</def> <specif>Hence:</specif> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>
<def>Inflated; full of boastful or insincere talk.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>passing intestinal gas excessively;
flatulent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

